modulePresetLibraryDesc: Create style or variables from well known design systems.
moduleVariableGeneratorDesc: Setup your local variables by code, say goodbye to time-consuming operation through official GUI.
destinationDesc1: Select where the variable(s) will be created.
destinationDesc2: Due to limitations of the plugin API, the list cannot instantly reflect all available collections when you use the plugin and the local variables window simultaneously. Please always refresh this tab to see the latest list.
variableModeDesc: Select under which mode will the variables being created.
valueTypeDesc: This is equivalent to all types figma has provided. The numbers are represent by FLOAT type.
variableScopeDesc: Select which scope will the variable being created apply.
codeEditorDesc1: The code should be an array, each element being an object with "name" and "value" properties to create a variable. Click the button below to generate example code. Click multiple times to create multiple variables.
codeEditorDesc2: Click the button below to generate example code. Click multiple times to create multiple variables.
moduleShortcutDesc: A comprehensive collection of various shortcut that will fasten your workflow.
generateHEXorRGB: Generate HEX or RGB text label
generateHEXorRGBDesc: To generate HEX or RGB value text label, you need to select layers that has fill color.
generateNoteDesignStatusTag: Generate Note, Design status tag, Title section
generateNoteDesignStatusTagDesc: To generate Note, Design status tag or Title section, you need to copy the template component into your file, then use the "Memorize" button with in setting window. After object is memorized, you can start generate these component instance by selecting one or multiple frames, then click generate button. The current date will be automatically fill in to the component by default.
moduleNamingClenerDesc: Clean the naming of layers within your selection.
renameAutoLayout: Auto layout: V Auto Layout / H Auto Layout
renameText: Text: The content of the text itself
moduleSelectionFilterDesc: Filter your selection with various of available options.
moduleVirtualProfileDesc: Virtual profile lets you easily unify and manage the dummy data used across your design.
editAndApplyDesc: You can edit the value by clicking the corresponding field. To apply the value, just select one or multiple layers, then click "Apply" button.
saveYourChangeDesc:
By default, the plugin will automatically save your changes. However, due to limitations of the plugin API, there might be occasions when your changes cannot be saved automatically.

To avoid any loss of your changes, it is recommended to always use the save button at the top of the page.
title: Title
modulePropertyClipboardDesc: Memorize specific property of selected object, then apply it to another object(s).
nothingInsideClipboard: There is nothing inside the clipboard.
name: Name
moduleSpaciiingDesc: Set spacing between elements with just one click.
customValueIsNotAffect: Custom value is not affected by multiply value.
designStatusTagHasNotBeenMemorized: The design status tag component has not been memorized. Please use the button below to memorize it.
noteHasNotBeenMemorized: The notes component has not been memorized. Please use the button below to memorize it.
titleSectionHasNotBeenMemorized: The title section component has not been memorized. Please use the button below to memorize it.
findAndReplaceCriteriaAreCaseSensitive: Find and replace criteria are case sensitive.
keepOriginalNameOfTextLayers: Keep original name of text layer(s)
howManyIconsToBeGenerated: How many icons to be generated
